Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.92,0:01:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,大家過來一下呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.24,0:01:57.97,Default,,80,80,0,,{\an3}什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.98,0:01:57.86,Default,,80,80,0,,{\an1}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,這一天又一天的　為什麼還要活著呢...
